data.description: SELLER WANT'S OFFERS, Price reduced $15K - HIGHLY MOTIVATED!  3/2 Pool home on the water with boat dock and direct access to the gulf.  Located in a nice neighborhood close to shopping and restaurants.  Home has been one owner occupied since being built.  No water or roof damage from the past hurricane Ian.  New a/c in 2018. Kitchen appliances need updating, dishwasher does not work from not being used for a period of time.  Indoor laundry room. Master bath has shower only and large walk in closet.  Guest bedroom has built in bed and wall unit.   Update this gem in the rough with new paint, appliances, and maybe some flooring and it will make this a very nice home or vacation rental.  Pool with under roof lanai is great for entertaining after coming back from a day of boating on this nice access canal.
